{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811960/extras/steam_img3.png?t=1735094392\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Two years ago in the autumn of 2043, a mysterious figure known as the \u201cShadow Reaper\u201d tore through the city-state of Calloway City before suddenly vanishing, taking 24 foreign Peacekeepers with him.\u00a0Almost a year later in the summer of 2044, the Shadow Reaper struck again, this time causing a whopping 32 members of the Calloway City senate to fall into a coma.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811960/extras/steam_1.png?t=1735094392\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Miss Audacity, a callow youth who witnessed Shadow Reaper in the act. Help her remember the key details of the case and bring the Reaper to justice!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you reach a happy ending in this tragic tale of loss, adversity, redemption, and self determination?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811960/extras/steam_img4.png?t=1735094392\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">This visual novel features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>World Without Reason:</strong> A story of loss, adversity, and redemption </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Nice Weekend Read:</strong> 5-6 hours for story completion</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Them's Fightin' Words:</strong>\u00a04 Boss fights and 1 verbal assault</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Putting a Voice to a Name:</strong> Partial voice acting for the main cast</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Erm, Actually:</strong> A full glossary containing all characters, locations, and tricky terminology </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Life Has Many Doors:</strong> 1 main ending, 6 alternate endings </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wall of Crazy:</strong> A chapter map showing all major events in chronological order</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>City of Secrets:</strong>\u00a0Calloway City is filled with mysteries, some of which are best left alone  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811960/extras/steam_img5.png?t=1735094392\" /></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Zero Logic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2811960/3afdfbe2d877fbbd78ff4373098c0567a34efee9.jpg"},{"name":"One Static Dream","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2811960/091f7abb8882753b9b80879116c6a7b6cecf20ae.jpg"},{"name":"Two Sisters","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2811960/696f76ebbe0fa1e0fd7ae98f146c3976c73d13be.jpg"},{"name":"Three Faded Memories","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2811960/97898798df177d5ee944981396bbd49eb1cd6aa6.jpg"},{"name":"For Want of Reason","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2811960/a4e18ff7bbaeaddf0cb99f0a76b1c580958b155d.jpg"},{"name":"Five Strikes Against Her","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2811960/91e51f13df48c9dbe94bce4b52c71889acff2942.jpg"},{"name":"siX","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2811960/1d052eb4d9e24c8ff0388f10b38a4905e30e84ca.jpg"},{"name":"Seven New Realities","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2811960/e88d48fbcff6e3ea185c63e624155caeaf81878f.jpg"},{"name":"Miss Genius Oshi","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/